{
  "SA14n1216:0": "XXIII",
  "SA14n1216:1": "śakraparivarto nāma trayoviṃśatitamaḥ |",
  "SA14n1216:2": "tena khalu punarityādi evaṃ śikṣamāṇaṃ cetyataḥ prāk |",
  "SA14n1216:3": "sadevamānuṣāsuraṃ lokaṃ sarvaśrāvakapratyekabuddhayānikānanupāyakuśalāṃśca bodhisattvo'bhibhavati |",
  "SA14n1216:4": "teṣāṃ cānabhibhūto bhavatīti pañcamī vivṛddhiḥ ||",
  "SA14n1216:5": "evaṃ śikṣamāṇaṃ cetyādi āparivartāntāt |",
  "SA14n1216:6": "catvāro lokapālāḥ śakrastadanye ca devāstamupasaṃkramiṣyantītyādibhiranuśaṃsaiḥ ṣaṣṭhī ||",
  "SA14n1216:7": "śakreṇoktaḥ parivartaḥ śakraparivartaḥ ||",
  "SA14n1216:8": "āryāṣṭasāhasrikāyāḥ prajñāpāramitāyāḥ sāratamānāmni pañjikāyāṃ ratnākaraśāntiviracitāyāṃ trayoviṃśatitamaḥ parivartaḥ ||"
}